Title: Scalar-Tensor Theory of Gravity on $M_4\times Z_{2}$ Geometry
Authors: Akira Kokado, Gaku Konisi, Takesi Saito and Yutaka Tada
Comments: 17 pages, LaTeX, no figures
Report-no: KG-PHYS-97005
\\
  In the Brans-Dicke(BD) theory on $M_{4}\times Z_{2}$ geometry the geometrical
meaning of the torsion is clarified. The BD theory on $M_{4}\times Z_{2}$ is
rederived by taking into account of a new isometry condition.
